title: Power Retouche Suite[ENG] [Full] [Photoshop Plugin]
description:
Best Photoshop plugins (Photoshop filters) for professional photo retouching

Photoshop plugin filters for high quality photo retouching and image editing by PowerRetouche
8 and 16 bit. Supports RGB, CMYK, Lab, Grayscale, Duotone.

 Windows version is for all versions of Photoshop, Elements, Fireworks, Paint Shop Pro, Corel Draw,
Illustrator and other software that supports Photoshop plugins. 
Compatible host applications for Windows versions:

Adobe Photoshop (Version 3 or higher)
 Adobe Photoshop Elements
 Adobe After Effects (Version 4.1 or higher, but not animatable)
 Adobe Illustrator (Version 7 and higher)
 Adobe ImageReady (Version 2 and higher)
 CDH Image Explorer Pro (Version 4 or higher)
 CiEBV Photoline 32 (Version 5 or higher)
 Corel Draw (Version 6 or higher)
 Corel PhotoPaint (Version 6 and higher). NOTE: Photopaint up to v. 9 can open 16 bit images, but does not support filtering in 16 bit, hence it disables plug-ins.
 Corel/Metacreations Painter (Version 6 and higher)
 Deneba Canvas (Version 6 or higher)
 imageN - freeware from http://www.pixoid.com/
 Jasc Paint Shop Pro (Version 4.12 or higher).
 Macromedia Freehand (Version 7 or higher)
 Macromedia Fireworks (Version 2 or higher)
 Mediachance PhotoBrush
 Megalux Ultimate Paint (Version 2 or higher)
 Megalux Ultimate FX (Adware from http://www.ultimatepaint.com/ufx/)
 Microfrontier Digital Darkroom (Version 1.2 or higher)
 Micrografx Picture Publisher (Version 8 or higher)
 Microsoft PhotoDraw 2000
 Newave Chaos Fx: Twillight'76 (Version 1.2 or higher)
 Picmaster (Version 1.25 and higher)
 Plugin Commander Pro (Version 1.5 or higher)
 QFX (Version 7 or higher)
 Right Hemisphere Deep Paint
 Satori PhotoXL (Version 2.29 or higher)
 Ulead PhotoImpact (Version 4 or higher)
